sh per year from large companies, but value the potential reward of equity much more than the guaranteed cash they'd be giving up to join a startup such as this. Job Responsibilities: - Building a developer platform similar to Hyperledger Fabric, using Stellar core as a reference architecture for the underlying blockchain transaction system. Creating an API for existing financial service products to use in order to move their operations onto the blockchain transaction system. - Integrating the company's cryptographic library (written in Rust), which enables new privacy/compliance tools, with a blockchain base layer for assets, accounts, smart contracts, transfers, etc. - Development of specialized financial apps such as exchanges, lending platforms, and investment funds on the underlying blockchain. - Architecting the process of large-scale deployment of the entire stack. - Executing quickly and effectively while keeping maintainability, large-scale systems design/architecture, and security as top priorities. Qualifications: - Experience doing the design and implementation of highly scalable and high performance platforms. - Experience distributed systems in a production environment - Strong programming skills in at least one of: Rust, C++, C, or Java - Willing to learn and primarily use Rust. - Understanding of security best practices - Great communication skills Nice to have: - Experience doing the planning and management of key product milestones - Experience with blockchain systems and/or cryptography - Experience with C++11 ? Did you like this job or want to see more?? All of our online job postings can be found on these sites: https://www.dice.com/company/10366547 https://www.monster.com/jobs/c-skyrocket-ventures.aspx https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/skyrocket-ventures-jobs Follow us on Instagram here: https://www.instagram.com/skyrocketventures Follow us on LinkedIn here: https://www.linkedin.com/company/skyrocket-ventures ",
